metadata.name: Kongo Golden Ape Society #1
metadata.description:
Ape #1 of Kongo Golden Ape Society, a thoroughly curated NTF collection of 500 unique high-class apes that hold value on the Ethereum blockchain. The extravagant jewelry, facial expressions and special trait types like rarity or appearance make up the particular hallmark of each ape, giving rise to collectible artworks without equal.

Developed by [Optryx Labs](https://optryx.io)
